alongside the one included with your operating system. This means if your Windows firewall misses something, VIPRE can catch it before it attacks your computer. It also has spam filtering and anti-phishing tools to cut down on schemes designed to steal your identity.","One of VIPRE&#39;s best tools is Social Watch. This function scans all information that attempts to sneak in through social media sites. This is important because it is easier for viruses and other threats to piggyback on news stories, links, images, games and videos shared through social media."]},"id":"f286b5c6-2219-4da1-8a6f-51a5758b8029","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Malware Protections"},"id":"484901c8-437a-4ae0-9ada-b73a9208d762","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["VIPRE doesn’t have parental controls, but you can block websites by setting the security levels in the privacy settings, much like the security settings on your internet browser. It also doesn’t have a password manager or safe banking tools that are typically included with the best internet security software.","Another drawback of VIPRE is that it doesn’t have mobile protection of any kind, so you will have to invest in a separate mobile protection program for your cellphones and tablets. If you would prefer an internet security program that is also compatible with mobile devices, consider <a href=\"/mcafee-review\">McAfee LiveSafe</a>.","VIPRE offers 24/7 live tech support via telephone. Plus, you can access other support tools, such as the FAQs and user community, through the support portal on the VIPRE website. You can also access chat support through the user portal."]},"id":"0ae9592d-0cf3-41f3-be38-9ce7f6446976","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"553889af-0457-4115-8db0-e978c8b19c1c","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The best tool of this internet security program is Social Watch, which stops new threats from sneaking in through social media networks. VIPRE is very effective at noticing new malware an